  "detailed_description": "<h1>Deceit 2: Master Bundle</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/0730432df6fdcac21229d660eda254cf.avif?t=1773077352\" width=748 height=896 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/05b68c3ab5d79f1383c77ebe6d9a7629.avif?t=1773077352\" width=780 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Deceit 2 is the online action PvP experience where your capacity for  trust and deception are put to the test. Join an ancient <strong>Ritual </strong>run by a twisted <strong>Game Master</strong>, claim your <strong>Role</strong> and work out how you can <strong>Escape</strong>. Do you have the skills to work out who’s with you and who’s against you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/4221d7615317100a8fe1f03668cc79ff.avif?t=1773077352\" width=780 height=118 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Three <strong>Teams </strong>go head-to-head; the <strong>Innocent</strong>, <strong>Infected </strong>and <strong>Cursed</strong>. However, nobody knows who is on their team and therefore: trust no one. <strong>Team </strong>up when it suits you, lie when it doesnâ€™t, and survive however you can. Every decision shapes how the nightmare unfolds, making every <strong>Ritual </strong>a unique story to tell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/d45d8d6511f890f07361c745360848ea.poster.avif?t=1773077352\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/d45d8d6511f890f07361c745360848ea.webm?t=1773077352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/d45d8d6511f890f07361c745360848ea.mp4?t=1773077352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/8fe6b77abe4cb630da284f1a65b17f3c.avif?t=1773077352\" width=780 height=118 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">The <strong>Ritual </strong>plays out across 5 unique locations, each steeped in atmosphere and danger. Each <strong>Ritual Site </strong>offers distinct layouts, challenging <strong>Tasks</strong>, and ultimately requires varied strategy if youâ€™re wanting to <strong>Escape</strong> before being <strong>Banished</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/0d1bf38160de51f2926fd2b6b75a5aa2.poster.avif?t=1773077352\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/0d1bf38160de51f2926fd2b6b75a5aa2.webm?t=1773077352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/0d1bf38160de51f2926fd2b6b75a5aa2.mp4?t=1773077352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/9e6a24cdef455a716f80dc6f6083879c.avif?t=1773077352\" width=780 height=118 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Around the<strong> Ritual Site</strong> youâ€™ll find <strong>Tasks </strong>which the <strong>Innocent </strong>must complete in order to <strong>Escape</strong>. The completion of these <strong>Tasks </strong>also unlock <strong>Items </strong>for the group at the <strong>Shop</strong>. Choose from <strong>Investigative</strong>, <strong>Offensive </strong>and <strong>Defensive </strong>tools which multiply the chaos, making each visit back to the <strong>Shop</strong> highly impactful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/13e40b9fc60843113ce9b0bc31eb353e.poster.avif?t=1773077352\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/13e40b9fc60843113ce9b0bc31eb353e.webm?t=1773077352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/13e40b9fc60843113ce9b0bc31eb353e.mp4?t=1773077352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/5ac87898f4b63c80f5030659ab4708cc.avif?t=1773077352\" width=780 height=118 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Climb the <strong>Ranks </strong>and prove your dominance in competitive play. Youâ€™ll be rewarded in your skills by unlocking exclusive rewards. Rise through <strong>Seasonal Leaderboards</strong> and challenge the strongest opponents to become a true <strong>Master of Deceit</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/7384412fc77ca5ee2ce8ac29dc2efca2.poster.avif?t=1773077352\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/7384412fc77ca5ee2ce8ac29dc2efca2.webm?t=1773077352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/7384412fc77ca5ee2ce8ac29dc2efca2.mp4?t=1773077352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/d6b9b865e21156f8ac232928520055c5.avif?t=1773077352\" width=780 height=118 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Participate as 1 of 9 <strong>Subjects </strong>trapped within the <strong>Ritual</strong>. Find your favourite, collect unlocks for them through <strong>Level Ups</strong> and customise their look inside the <strong>Collection</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/8904cb13696af380bc2614f6fae41c5b.poster.avif?t=1773077352\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/8904cb13696af380bc2614f6fae41c5b.webm?t=1773077352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/8904cb13696af380bc2614f6fae41c5b.mp4?t=1773077352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
